rComments: Nice guy that cares but he's not great at teaching. This was his first time teaching and it was pretty easy to tell. He didn't seem prepared and when he'd give in class tutorials, it was like he was seeing the stuff for the first time. Assignments were really easy as long as you follow the instructions and watched the tutorials

Prof Seifollahi makes his class easy. Show up to class (or watch recordings) and you are sure to pass the class easily. For whatever reason, final exam was harder than expected, but it may be because the whole year was easy. He ensures you can easily pass all projects and spends considerable amount of time going through the projects step by step.
The professor takes his time during lectures. The assignments and midterms are fair !
